//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FOO_FIGHTERS_LONDON_STADIUM_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FOO_FIGHTERS_LONDON_STADIUM_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于危险的天气条件，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">喷火战机</a>在皇后区的演唱会被取消后发表了一份声明 - 看看乐队在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/foo-fighters-live-in-manchester-setlist-photos-3765719">喷火战机生活在曼彻斯特：所向无敌，仍然不可撼动</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（7 月 17 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">Dave Grohl</a>等人。前往纽约皇后区的花旗球场，观看该场馆两场演出中的第一场。然而，由于露天体育场上空的大雨和闪电，演出突然结束，乐队只演奏了通常 20 多首歌曲中的 13 首歌曲。</p><p>据现场人士透露，格罗尔警告与会者，如果即将到来的风暴在表演“学习飞行”之前继续恶化，演出可能会被缩短。随后，乐队在节目正式剪辑之前表演了《Everlong》的前奏。 </p><figure id="attachment_3766584" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3766584" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3766584" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270.jpg" alt="喷火战机乐队的戴夫·格罗尔（左）和乔什·弗里斯（右）将于 2024 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Foo-Fighters@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3766584" class="wp-caption-text">喷火战机乐队的戴夫·格罗尔（左）和乔什·弗里斯（右）将于 2024 年表演。图片来源：Paul Morigi/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>该乐队将于周五（7 月 19 日）再次在该场地演出，他们写道：“我们非常失望，无法为今晚花旗球场的精彩观众演奏全套曲目。但我们的球迷、工作人员和体育场内工作人员的安全是第一位的，所以当确定在这种危险的天气下没有安全的方法继续演出时，我们别无选择，只能到此为止。”</p><p>他们继续说道：“我们很感激能够为你们踢球的每一秒，并期待再次见到你们——也许最快就在周五！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9jHi8gp8Da/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.